# 💰 Finance Backend API

![Python](https://img.shields.io/badge/Python-3.10+-blue?logo=python)
![Django](https://img.shields.io/badge/Django-5.2-green?logo=django)
![DRF](https://img.shields.io/badge/DRF-REST_Framework-red?logo=django)
![License](https://img.shields.io/badge/license-MIT-yellow)
![Status](https://img.shields.io/badge/status-In%20Development-orange)

> A **Django + Django REST Framework** API built for **personal finance management**.  
> It lets users manage **accounts**, **categories**, and **transactions** (income and expenses) with **JWT authentication**, filtering, pagination, and **Swagger documentation** powered by `drf-spectacular`.

---

## 🚀 Technologies

- 🐍 **Python 3.10+**
- ⚙️ **Django 5.2**
- 🧩 **Django REST Framework**
- 🔒 **JWT Authentication (SimpleJWT)**
- 📊 **drf-spectacular** (Swagger + OpenAPI)
- 🌐 **CORS Headers**
- 🧠 **SQLite** (for local development)

---

## 🧱 API Structure

### 🔐 Authentication
| Method | Endpoint | Description |
|:-------|:----------|:------------|
| `POST` | `/api/auth/register/` | Register a new user |
| `POST` | `/api/auth/token/` | Generate access and refresh tokens |
| `POST` | `/api/auth/token/refresh/` | Refresh access token |
| `GET`  | `/api/auth/me/` | Get current logged-in user info |

---

### 💼 Accounts
| Method | Endpoint | Description |
|:-------|:----------|:------------|
| `GET` | `/api/accounts/` | List all user accounts |
| `POST` | `/api/accounts/` | Create a new account |
| `PUT` | `/api/accounts/{id}/` | Update an account |
| `DELETE` | `/api/accounts/{id}/` | Delete an account |

---

### 🗂️ Categories
| Method | Endpoint | Description |
|:-------|:----------|:------------|
| `GET` | `/api/categories/` | List categories (filterable by type) |
| `POST` | `/api/categories/` | Create a new category |
| `PUT` | `/api/categories/{id}/` | Update a category |
| `DELETE` | `/api/categories/{id}/` | Delete a category |

---

### 💸 Transactions
| Method | Endpoint | Description |
|:-------|:----------|:------------|
| `GET` | `/api/transactions/` | List transactions (with filters) |
| `POST` | `/api/transactions/` | Create a new transaction |
| `PUT` | `/api/transactions/{id}/` | Update a transaction |
| `DELETE` | `/api/transactions/{id}/` | Delete a transaction |

#### ⚠️ Validation Rules
- Transactions **cannot have value ≤ 0**
- Transaction `type` must match the category’s type  
  _(Example: type = “INCOME” → category type must also be “INCOME”)_

---

### 📊 Financial Summary
| Method | Endpoint | Description |
|:-------|:----------|:------------|
| `GET` | `/api/summary/` | Returns balance, total income, total expenses, and totals per category |

**Example Response:**
```json
{
  "balance": 2964.10,
  "income": 3000.0,
  "expenses": 35.9,
  "by_category": [
    {"category": "Salary", "total": 3000.0},
    {"category": "Food", "total": 35.9}
  ]
}
